\n基本上開風扇定冷氣都唔怕<br />\n因為R唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但事前準備非常麻煩 <br />\n晚晚都搞半粒鐘先訓得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf05ae801eff8a523e849971a9813505d45ec4d9","tid":701121,"uid":52132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:17:00.000Z","msg":"冷氣2個鐘後自動閂"},{"pid":"217f086ead4e209cbcad5284f2496c8576bd47c4","tid":701121,"uid":25502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:29:47.000Z","msg":"想知有冇巴打睇過吳x輝醫生, 佢醫皮膚好似好掂咁"},{"pid":"3e89e3be50b29fe19ddda74728a4444ce55a1693","tid":701121,"uid":127759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e93f6d6b5aeb7afc227710cc9cfcedccf1af700","tid":701121,"uid":170062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:11:38.000Z","msg":"我近期用咗濕敷包紮 <br />\n濕疹好番好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:38:50.000Z","msg":"講黎聽下係點得唔得"},{"pid":"768d5d14ce1e7a6190c623e5c796be20a3749fe9","tid":701121,"uid":46566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"217f086ead4e209cbcad5284f2496c8576bd47c4","tid":701121,"uid":25502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:29:47.000Z","msg":"想知有冇巴打睇過吳x輝醫生, 佢醫皮膚好似好掂咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:45:50.000Z","msg":"全名係咩"},{"pid":"6b1938a94e76255bc5d585a40fbc32b8e5aa4457","tid":701121,"uid":170062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e89e3be50b29fe19ddda74728a4444ce55a1693","tid":701121,"uid":127759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e93f6d6b5aeb7afc227710cc9cfcedccf1af700","tid":701121,"uid":170062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:11:38.000Z","msg":"我近期用咗濕敷包紮 <br />\n濕疹好番好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:38:50.000Z","msg":"講黎聽下係點得唔得"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:51:03.000Z","msg":"我既濕疹近排係好厲害啦<br />\n腳眼位圍住一個圈都係損咗流血既濕疹<br />\n咁無辦法之下 我就沖完涼<br />\n用咗一層好薄既類固醇先 <br />\n跟著再厚敷凡士林 <br />\n外面再用濕咗莞茜水既紗布圍住<br />\n最後用崩帶包紮 <br />\n<br />\n第一日搽咗類固醇係好得好快<br />\n第二日見傷口埋咗 就整係用凡士林厚敷<br />\n之後再用加咗死海鹽既莞茜水濕敷 <br />\n<br />\n而家基本上只得紅印 <br />\n神奇地唔包果時都唔會想R <br />\n<br />\n另外近排有飲五花茶 <br />\n同食一d幫助排便既supplement <br />\n就好似好番好多喇！  <br />\n <br />\n可能唔係個個受得我依招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我知濕敷對濕疹係好有幫助既"},{"pid":"5172d0bc3b63a11dd18f29727a2f50b8c8d2f098","tid":701121,"uid":25502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"768d5d14ce1e7a6190c623e5c796be20a3749fe9","tid":701121,"uid":46566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"217f086ead4e209cbcad5284f2496c8576bd47c4","tid":701121,"uid":25502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:29:47.000Z","msg":"想知有冇巴打睇過吳x輝醫生, 佢醫皮膚好似好掂咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:45:50.000Z","msg":"全名係咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351dd648461b2c0a8d347c9d510932f9f6cb28ee","tid":701121,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:01:48.000Z","msg":"25度冷氣 床邊放杯水"},{"pid":"8e1551eb3fb0ef7450f4adff5e0dfbf5757ae55c","tid":701121,"uid":25502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b1938a94e76255bc5d585a40fbc32b8e5aa4457","tid":701121,"uid":170062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e89e3be50b29fe19ddda74728a4444ce55a1693","tid":701121,"uid":127759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e93f6d6b5aeb7afc227710cc9cfcedccf1af700","tid":701121,"uid":170062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:11:38.000Z","msg":"我近期用咗濕敷包紮 <br />\n濕疹好番好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:38:50.000Z","msg":"講黎聽下係點得唔得"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:51:03.000Z","msg":"我既濕疹近排係好厲害啦<br />\n腳眼位圍住一個圈都係損咗流血既濕疹<br />\n咁無辦法之下 